OL,3,CBurnham urged to reverse national
OL,4,Cinsurance rise costing firms #1,000
OL,5,Cper worker
OL,7,FThe Chancellor's decision to raise
OL,8,Femployers' national insurance is
OL,9,Fcosting the average business more than
OL,10,F#1,000 per worker every year, figures
OL,11,Fshow.
OL,13,FFor those on the real living wage,
OL,14,Fwhich amounts to a full-time salary of
OL,15,Fabout #26,228 a year, employers are
OL,16,Fpaying an average of #890 extra in tax
OL,17,Fa year, according to analysis by the
OL,18,FScottish Parliament Information Centre
OL,19,F(SPICe).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
