OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783792086
OL,3,CBurnham urged to reverse national
OL,4,Cinsurance rise costing firms #1,000
OL,5,Cper worker
OL,7,FThe figure rises to #1,053 for those
OL,8,Fearning the Scottish median wage of
OL,9,F#39,879.
OL,11,FThe SNP, which commissioned the
OL,12,Fanalysis, called for Andy Burnham, who
OL,13,Fis expected to become prime minister
OL,14,Flater this month, to reverse the
OL,15,Femployers' national insurance rise.
OL,17,FChancellor Rachel Reeves raised the
OL,18,Frate of national insurance, and
OL,19,Flowered the tax's starting threshold,
OL,20,Fin 2024 after Labour won a landslide
OL,21,Felection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
