OL,3,CBurnham urged to reverse national
OL,4,Cinsurance rise costing firms #1,000
OL,5,Cper worker
OL,7,FSNP MSP Laura Mitchell said: "Andy
OL,8,FBurnham must, as a priority, scrap the
OL,9,FLabour Party's national insurance tax
OL,10,Fhike, which has destroyed jobs and
OL,11,Fcost Scotland's businesses huge sums
OL,12,Fof money.
OL,14,F"This was an incredibly short-sighted
OL,15,FLabour Government policy which has
OL,16,Fcreated a high-cost, toxic environment
OL,17,Ffor businesses across Scotland and the
OL,18,FUK ` cutting jobs, squeezing wages,
OL,19,Freducing investment and choking off
OL,20,Feconomic growth.
OL,26,@oD@^OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
