OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783792086
OL,3,CBurnham urged to reverse national
OL,4,Cinsurance rise costing firms #1,000
OL,5,Cper worker
OL,7,F"Analysis now shows that this policy
OL,8,Fis costing business in Scotland around
OL,9,F#1,000 per employee ` is it any wonder
OL,10,Fwhy employment is up and fewer
OL,11,Fvacancies are opening. That is the
OL,12,Fcost of Westminster.
OL,14,F"Westminster policies have wiped
OL,15,Fbillions of pounds from Scotland's
OL,16,Feconomy, causing unemployment and the
OL,17,Fcost of living to soar.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
