OL,3,CBurnham urged to reverse national
OL,4,Cinsurance rise costing firms #1,000
OL,5,Cper worker
OL,7,F"It's clear Scotland needs the full
OL,8,Fpowers of independence so we can build
OL,9,Fa stronger economy and a better
OL,10,Ffuture."
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Mr Burnham said:
OL,13,F"Andy is focused on delivering good
OL,14,Fgrowth in every postcode, raising
OL,15,Fliving standards and giving families
OL,16,Fbreathing space by tackling rising
OL,17,Fcosts. On tax, he is committed to the
OL,18,Fmanifesto."
